{"type": "article", "id": 7587, "title": "Aljoud Lootah 折叠家具", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-20T07:31:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234809VQePUvx7aqKLJu1N.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t这是阿联酋女设计师 Aljoud Lootah 为 2015 年迪拜设计日推出的一组作品，这个名为 Oru 的系列作品灵感来源自日本的折纸艺术，而 “Oru” 也正是日语里面“折叠”的意思。这一组作品包括一个台灯，一个椅子，一个装饰镜和一个橱柜。Aljoud Lootah 试图通过这组作品表达“简单的纸张可以折叠出无限的世界”这一理念。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234805O2NLMg1enHEzsKbl.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.74259259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234806zs6dAuiQn739Sm4k.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.69351852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234806aUlCsW0VREcj8Ppx.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.63703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052348073DlZAP9iC0X71Jrv.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.69722222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234807kbYxuWNOB5oaXFTP.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.64259259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234808pg9UHDX2